{"tid":1460983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【極重要　幫推上頂】即使林鄭答應一兩項訴求　香港人必須不撤不散　直至美國通過《香港人權與民主法案》","createTime":"2019-08-13T05:42:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:38:17.000Z","uid":14328,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9762a920f58e6f26cc50ac16ec962f8694c4ce9a","tid":1460983,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:42:32.000Z","msg":"《香港人權與民主法案》<br />\n民主黨 &amp; 共和黨 已經有哂共識<br />\n係而家呢個情況　呢條法案只要一提上去<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">必定會通過</span></span><br />\n<br />\n通過之後<br />\n<br />\n美國可以凍結中國／香港官員海外資產<br />\n實施經濟制裁<br />\n保障香港人雙普選權利<br />\n<br />\n呢條法案，係真真正正對中國／香港當權者唯一具有極大制衡力嘅法案<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係香港人未來嘅護身符</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以我希望大家，就算林鄭話撤回修例、成立獨立調查委員會。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人必須頂到美國國會復會，直至美國通過《香港人權與民主法案》</span></span><br />\n<br />\n好重要，求求大家幫推上頂"},{"pid":"1099a0df7a6a4a137e51367351d3cae0e14a1d7c","tid":1460983,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:43:22.000Z","msg":"ｎｅｖｅｒ　ｆｏｒｇｅｔ　７２１　８１１<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597c8e4df0be70ba18beb76ea6ee7539825cab43","tid":1460983,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:46:03.000Z","msg":"頂住"},{"pid":"f798bf2d51ced72a7e27a508e8118a0ce2204201","tid":1460983,"uid":19634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:48:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff1beb15aa7eaf27184d5764403b64c02445602","tid":1460983,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:50:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />